<body>
<cb:div>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<pb n="0164a" xml:id="I01.0065.0164a" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0164a00" type="honorific"/><cb:docNumber>No. 65</cb:docNumber>
<lb ed="I" n="0164a00" type="honorific"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"></cb:mulu><cb:jhead><title>宋敬業等造塔記</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="I" n="0164a01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0164a0101">曦望晷速。三曜不停。春還秋往。陰陽<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">貿</unclear><note n="0164001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30634"/>＝遷【史】</note><note n="0164001" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30634"/>【佛拓】，遷【史】</note><app n="0164001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">遷</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30634"/></rdg></app>。有始
<lb ed="I" n="0164a02" type="honorific"/>將終。有生必滅。唯无上大覺。<note n="0164002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">躰＝體【史】</note><note n="0164002" resp="ihp" type="mod">躰【佛拓】，體【史】</note><app n="0164002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">體</lem><rdg wit="【原】">躰</rdg></app>宿常湛。故使人
<lb ed="I" n="0164a03" type="honorific"/>知覆護。勿識皈依。是乃佛弟子　宋敬業。崔<note n="0164003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB13426"/>＝海【史】</note><note n="0164003" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB13426"/>【佛拓】，海【史】</note><app n="0164003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">海</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB13426"/></rdg></app>
<lb ed="I" n="0164a04" type="honorific"/>寶。郭小德。張<note n="0164004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB01739"/>＝燕【史】</note><note n="0164004" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB01739"/>【佛拓】，燕【史】</note><app n="0164004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">燕</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB01739"/></rdg></app>子等。洞識苦空。<note n="0164005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30751"/>＝淵【史】</note><note n="0164005" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30751"/>【佛拓】，淵【史】</note><app n="0164005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">淵</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30751"/></rdg></app>知八解。兼識
<lb ed="I" n="0164a05" type="honorific"/>財稱不<note n="0164006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30952"/>＝聚【史】</note><note n="0164006" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30952"/>【佛拓】，聚【史】</note><app n="0164006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">聚</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30952"/></rdg></app>。身名假合。見<note n="0164007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30953"/>＝蘆【史】</note><note n="0164007" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30953"/>【佛拓】，蘆【史】</note><app n="0164007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">蘆</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30953"/></rdg></app>葦之空虛。知<note n="0164008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30954"/>＝芭【史】</note><note n="0164008" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30954"/>【佛拓】，芭【史】</note><app n="0164008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">芭</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30954"/></rdg></app>蕉之
<lb ed="I" n="0164a06" type="honorific"/>匪實。何以逢除厚彰。輕<note n="0164009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30955"/>＝拔【史】</note><note n="0164009" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30955"/>【佛拓】，拔【史】</note><app n="0164009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">拔</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30955"/></rdg></app>无明。方欲寄<note n="0164010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30956"/>＝煎【史】</note><note n="0164010" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30956"/>【佛拓】，煎【史】</note><app n="0164010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">煎</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30956"/></rdg></app>三毒
<lb ed="I" n="0164a07" type="honorific"/>之苦。永入解脫之門。因茲勝地。建无上之功。
<lb ed="I" n="0164a08" type="honorific"/>大齊天保九年歲次戊寅三月甲午<note n="0164011" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30957"/>＝朔【史】</note><note n="0164011" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30957"/>【佛拓】，朔【史】</note><app n="0164011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">朔</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30957"/></rdg></app>六日癸
<lb ed="I" n="0164a09" type="honorific"/><note n="0164012" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30958"/>＝亥【史】</note><note n="0164012" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30958"/>【佛拓】，亥【史】</note><app n="0164012"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">亥</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30958"/></rdg></app>。仰為廣固南寺大眾等。敬造寶塔一<note n="0164013" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30959"/>＝區【史】</note><note n="0164013" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30959"/>【佛拓】，區【史】</note><app n="0164013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">區</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30959"/></rdg></app>。万刃
<lb ed="I" n="0164a10" type="honorific"/>名山。峭崿峙其北。清<note n="0164014" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">渕＝淵【史】</note><note n="0164014" resp="ihp" type="mod">渕【佛拓】，淵【史】</note><app n="0164014"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">淵</lem><rdg wit="【原】">渕</rdg></app>淥池。遄流<note n="0164015" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30934"/>＝旋【史】</note><note n="0164015" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30934"/>【佛拓】，旋【史】</note><app n="0164015"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">旋</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30934"/></rdg></app>其前。神仙之
<lb ed="I" n="0164a11" type="honorific"/>宮詎得方其麗。踴出鑽天可以比其暉。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">崇</unclear>斯<note n="0164016" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">稫＝福【史】</note><note n="0164016" resp="ihp" type="mod">稫【佛拓】，福【史】</note><app n="0164016"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">福</lem><rdg wit="【原】">稫</rdg></app>
<lb ed="I" n="0164a12" type="honorific"/>□仰資七世。儗入閑門。龍登<note n="0164017" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB08660"/>＝初【史】</note><note n="0164017" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB08660"/>【佛拓】，初【史】</note><app n="0164017"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">初</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB08660"/></rdg></app>會。<app type="star" corresp="#0164009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">拔</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30955"/></rdg></app>潤現存。超
<lb ed="I" n="0164a13" type="honorific"/>□□位。　帝祚長<note n="0164018" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30741"/>＝延【史】</note><note n="0164018" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30741"/>【佛拓】，延【史】</note><app n="0164018"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">延</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30741"/></rdg></app>。法界蒙澤。<note n="0164019" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">茖＝若【史】</note><note n="0164019" resp="ihp" type="mod">茖【佛拓】，若【史】</note><app n="0164019"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">若</lem><rdg wit="【原】">茖</rdg></app>不刊石流芳。
<lb ed="I" n="0164a14" type="honorific"/>□□易滅。其頌曰。
<lb ed="I" n="0164a15" type="honorific"/>□灼法炬。晃朗慧日。悟<note n="0164020" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">佊＝彼【史】</note><note n="0164020" resp="ihp" type="mod">佊【佛拓】，彼【史】</note><app n="0164020"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">彼</lem><rdg wit="【原】">佊</rdg></app>迷徒。出茲闇室。門稱
<lb ed="I" n="0164a16" type="honorific"/>不二。義唯歸一。位登无上。果緣周畢。麗同玉室。
<lb ed="I" n="0164a17" type="honorific"/>□似銀宮。彫曦漏月。鐸嚮從風。將如地踊。<app type="star" corresp="#0164019"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">若</lem><rdg wit="【原】">茖</rdg></app>現
<lb ed="I" n="0164a18" type="honorific"/>空中。恃斯勝善。同履虛沖。</p>
